implementation_notes:
=== COMMON PATTERNS ===

Get trigger body field safely:
  @triggerBody()?['data']?['id']

Current item property in ForEach:
  @items('For_each')?['name']

Build ISO timestamp for API query:
  @formatDateTime(addDays(utcNow(), -7), 'yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ')

Conditional value:
  @if(equals(body('HTTP')?['status'], 'active'), 'Yes', 'No')

Coalesce null fields:
  @coalesce(body('HTTP')?['displayName'], body('HTTP')?['mail'], 'Unknown')

Parse JSON string to object:
  @json(body('HTTP'))

Get array length:
  @length(body('HTTP')?['value'])

Format number as string with padding:
  @concat('000', string(variables('counter')))
  (then use substring for fixed width)

Previous month first day:
  @startOfMonth(addToTime(utcNow(), -1, 'Month'))

Quarter calculation (1-4):
  @add(div(sub(int(formatDateTime(utcNow(), 'MM')), 1), 3), 1)
